{"tid":2159733,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"譚耀宗譚惠珠，呢鋪我撐你","createTime":"2020-08-16T13:21:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T07:36:55.000Z","uid":58335,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fe83faa8f35f5af9819d9978ee42e700c5069b65","tid":2159733,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T13:21:14.000Z","msg":"比人睇穿晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全國人大常委譚耀宗昨稱，民主派應會接受延任，<span class=\"red\">「總辭、杯葛，我認為應該唔會發生，佢自己都好大損失㗎嘛。」民主派只不過不想即時答應，否則會予人感覺不捨得議席，加上接受延任或受到抗爭派批評</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，又指希望有關議員不要再做以前的行為，勸喻重新做人。 基本法委員會副主任譚惠珠指，<span class=\"red\">民主派會找到理由返回議會</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但呼籲對方「守法」，包括港版國安法。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200814/G36NKJBWWRED3AMAGLOVBH5TEI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200814%2FG36NKJBWWRED3AMAGLOVBH5TEI%2F&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJDYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=0bd3053b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200814%2FG36NKJBWWRED3AMAGLOVBH5TEI%2F&h=c8b70616\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200814/G36NKJBWWRED3AMAGLOVBH5TEI/</a>"},{"pid":"26db47d833d392f16945a6a2e1cea460fd83c513","tid":2159733,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T15:57:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ac53dc9ca9a4fb6f076a303ec98c39062085ed9","tid":2159733,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T16:00:41.000Z","msg":"找到理由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n重新做人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e0ea046705d50fd742706d0aa37fd7feea14109","tid":2159733,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T06:45:39.000Z","m